snippet.title: Staring Time - Official Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Check out the unsettling trailer for Staring Time and get a peek at this psychological horror game. An extended demo for Staring Time will be available on itch.io on October 28, 2023.
